Cybertronian Fire doesn't exist anymore. You didn't know that, 
because I haven't updated the map recently. I'm updating right now, 
but I don't know what the maximal base is called called. =( (It'll be 
the Maximal City on the map when I'm done.)


On 26 Jun 2001, at 1:29, Nicolas Marion wrote:

> After a long journey, the dragon arrived to his destination. Although
> he had never seen it or heard of it, he knew that this was
> Cybertronian Fire, the maximal's base. He could not say why, he just
> felt it in his spark...
> 
> AzureBlade:
> So this is where my fellow Maximals have established... Nice design!
> But the main thing is that I have found them!
> 
> He transformed to his robot mode and landed in front of the base.
> 
> AzureBlade:
> (His voice was louder because of the echo)
> Fellow Maximals! My name is AzureBlade and I wish to join you in your
> fight against the Predacons!
